f. Notice of Financial Incentive
Members of Tropic Rewards may receive points for every dollar spent on qualifying purchases and via participation in periodic additional points-earning opportunities.  Points may be accumulated and redeemed for purchases of eligible products. We collect Personal Information in connection with providing Tropic Rewards to consumers.  This includes the following categories of Personal Information:
Identifiers such as name, postal and email addresses, internet protocol (IP) address, unique personal identifier, online identifier and token identifier when you submit your information to create an account with us, join Tropic Rewards, interact with us on social media, or sign up to learn more about our products and services.
The following categories of protected classification characteristics under California or federal law: birthdate when you sign up to receive special offers as part of Tropic Rewards.
Commercial information such as purchases you have made and use of loyalty program rewards.
You are given the choice to opt-in to Tropic Rewards when you register for an account in the Tropical Smoothie Cafe App. You may withdraw from Tropic Rewards at any time on the Tropical Smoothie Cafe App. We benefit financially from Tropic Rewards through increased customer loyalty, but we do not assign an independent monetary value to the Personal Information we collect in connection with Tropic Rewards. We estimate in good faith that the value of the Personal Information that we collect through Tropic Rewards would be less than the value that Tropic Rewards provides to consumers. To the extent that we calculate the value of the Personal Information we collect through Tropic Rewards, we do so in good faith based on the expenses related to the collection and retention of Personal Information in connection with Tropic Rewards.
